    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<h2>Veska Maelan — Trade-Clearing Notary, Hardby</h2>\n<p><em>Caelith Dunivar's Hardby contact. Reads the Aerdi clearing-marks better than anyone outside the firms themselves. The investigative gateway of Phase 3 — her notarial opinion turns the recovered evidence into a court-admissible package.</em></p>\n<h3>Description</h3>\n<p>Mid-fifties, Hardby-born, compact build, gray hair worn short under a soft brown cap. Plain wool dress, no jewelry except a small silver scale-and-scroll badge at the throat (her notarial seal of office). Reading lenses on a black silk cord. Quiet, watchful, slow-moving — the kind of professional whose stillness reads as authority.</p>\n<h3>Combat behavior</h3>\n<p><strong>Will not fight.</strong> Veska is a notary, not a combatant. If pressed she yields and offers her notarial seal in trade for her safety; she will reconstruct any document she has yielded once she is safe. Her value is in her head and in her files; killing her costs the party three of the most important investigative leads in Phase 3.</p>\n<h3>Statblock summary (CR 1, PB +2)</h3>\n<p><strong>AC</strong> 11 · <strong>HP</strong> 22 (5d8) · <strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft. · <strong>Init</strong> +0 · <strong>Passive Perception</strong> 15</p>\n<p><strong>STR</strong> 10 (+0) · <strong>DEX</strong> 11 (+0) · <strong>CON</strong> 12 (+1) · <strong>INT</strong> 18 (+4) · <strong>WIS</strong> 16 (+3) · <strong>CHA</strong> 14 (+2)</p>\n<p><strong>Saves:</strong> INT +6, WIS +5.</p>\n<p><strong>Skills:</strong> History +6, Insight +5, Investigation +8, Perception +5, Persuasion +4.</p>\n<p><strong>Senses:</strong> Passive Perception 15. <strong>Languages:</strong> Common, Old Aerdi, one trade cipher (Yeomanry diplomatic, current).</p>\n<h3>Traits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Reader of Hands.</strong> Veska can identify the writer of a document, the chop applied to it, and the era and provenance of the wax used to seal it, with up to a week's careful comparison work against her own files.</li>\n<li><strong>Notarial Standing.</strong> Her sworn notarial opinions are admissible in any Aerdi or Yeomanry court without further authentication.</li>\n<li><strong>Quiet Network.</strong> Veska maintains correspondence with eight other notaries across the Aerdi coast, all in cipher. She can request and receive a comparison-document from any of them within ten days.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Source</h3>\n<p><em>Blooming Rot, Part 2 — Phase 3.</em> See <em>Hardby NPCs → Veska Maelan</em> for full profile and approach phrase.</p>",
        "public": ""
      },
